						<h3>Ditch fats that are solid at room temperature

</h3>
						<p>Switch to the healthy fats such as olive oil, sunflower oil and canola oil that stay in a liquid form when stored in the cupboard. But all fats have a high caloric density, so just use what you need for cooking and salad dressings.

</p>
